          <actionDate>2014-09-10</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Stop Funding Terrorism Act - Prohibits any direct U.S. assistance, loan guarantee, or debt relief to the Palestinian Authority (PA) or any affiliated governing entity or leadership organization.</p> <p>States that such prohibition shall have no effect for a fiscal year if the President certifies to Congress that the PA has: </p> <ul> <li>formally recognized Israel's right to exist as a Jewish state and publicly recognized the state of Israel, </li> <li>renounced terrorism and purged all individuals with terrorist ties from the security services, </li> <li>terminated funding of anti-American and anti-Israel incitement, </li> <li>publicly pledged to not engage in war with Israel, and </li> <li>honored previous diplomatic agreements.</li></ul>]]></text>
